text: Phri jab Allah Taalaa unn ko bacha leta hai to foran hi woh zamin mein na haq sirkashi kerney lagtay hain aey logo! Yeh tumhari sirkashi tumharay liye wabaal honey wali hai dunyawi zindagi kay (chand) faeeday hain phir humaray pass tum ko aana hai phir hum sab tumhara kiya hua tum ko batla den gay
